Introduction

I selected Instagram for this Software Requirements Specification (SRS) because it is one of the applications that I use daily.

Instagram is a social media platform that allows users to share photos, videos, reels, and stories. Users can also interact with each other through likes, comments, follows, and direct messages.

This document describes the functional and technical requirements of the Instagram application. It will help developers, testers, and stakeholders understand the expected behavior of the system.



Purpose

The purpose of this SRS document is to define the software requirements of Instagram and provide a clear understanding of the application's features and functionality.

This document will be used during development and testing activities.


Scope

The scope of this project includes:

- User Registration
- Login and Logout
- Profile Management
- Create Post
- Stories
- Reels
- Follow and Unfollow
- Like and Comment
- Direct Messaging
- Change Password


